snippet.textDisplay:
The music creation depicts Devi Sati set herself ablaze on fire after her father Daksha insulted her husband Bhagwan Shiva by not calling him in Yagna.

Song beautifully captures the incident and as it's result - the rage and sadness of Lord Shiva after getting to know that Sati is no more..

This creation is on repeat mode for more than a month in my device now. This creation is divine, has so much emotions and intensity to it. Goosebumps and tears everytime I hear this. May bhagwan Shiva bless all the artists, and us! AUM NAMAH SHIVAY! AUM SHANTIHI!
